Issues.Body:
In custom directive, update hook parameter 'el' is giving all elements used by directive! I have following code - 

component 1:
`<button v-spinner="var1" @click="toggleVar1()">Button 1</button>`
component 2:
`<button v-spinner="var2" @click="toggleVar2()">Button 2</button>`

`toggleVar1()` and `toggleVar2()` functions toggles the boolean values of variables `var1` and `var2` respectively.
```
//global directive for bind and update together
Vue.directive('spinner', function (el, binding) {
    console.log(el);
});
```
I just want only changed element! Not all!

